00:28:50,360 --> 00:28:53,380
people's you only go to the property through the person. And if

589
00:28:53,380 --> 00:28:56,380
you can't prove which person pays you money, owes you money, you

590
00:28:56,380 --> 00:28:58,959
can't go straight to the property. וכולא כלשנא קמא *V'chol k'lishna kama*,

591
00:28:58,959 --> 00:29:02,020
then basically etc. And then the rest of the סוגיא *Suggya* continues

592
00:29:02,020 --> 00:29:05,360
like before and in the end the conclusion is is that the

593
00:29:05,360 --> 00:29:08,480
father died, there's a lien on the estate and then they split

594
00:29:08,480 --> 00:29:12,680
and the question is does that translate into only collecting half and

595
00:29:12,680 --> 00:29:14,459
then we'd say חמש ולא חצי חמש *Chamesh velo chatzi chamesh*, or

596
00:29:14,459 --> 00:29:17,740
does that allow based on various assumptions that you're able to are

597
00:29:17,740 --> 00:29:20,820
allowed to collect equally from both, fully from both brothers and that

598
00:29:20,820 --> 00:29:24,700
would be חמש ואפילו חמש *Chamesh v'afillu chamesh* and then you would

599
00:29:24,700 --> 00:29:27,400
be collecting the full five. And again, the interesting conceptual point here

600
00:29:27,400 --> 00:29:32,160
is is that the ritual obligation derives from the loan and if

601
00:29:32,160 --> 00:29:34,540
there's no way you can exact the loan then there's no ritual

602
00:29:34,540 --> 00:29:39,240
obligation. But even that being said, it's not purely a loan because

603
00:29:39,240 --> 00:29:41,020
if it was less than five, it was two and a half,

604
00:29:41,020 --> 00:29:43,000
you wouldn't have to pay it. If it was purely a loan,

605
00:29:43,000 --> 00:29:44,540
you'd have to pay two and a half. So there are some

606
00:29:44,540 --> 00:29:47,740
limits based on sort of the ritual framing of it but nevertheless

607
00:29:47,740 --> 00:29:52,440
the basic obligation hinges on the sort of civil obligation and we'll

608
00:29:52,440 --> 00:29:55,260
continue with this and I think people have had enough. But tomorrow

609
00:29:55,260 --> 00:29:57,520
we'll also maybe go a little further.
